fields.customfield_17816:
INSTRUCTIONS for submitting an NSV Purchase Request using this form:
1. Summary - Summary box above, type a brief description of what needs to be purchased and for what purpose. Example: “Cables and optics required for Multinode cluster”
2. Delivery Date Needed – Select the date you need the equipment by. Plan for at least 3 days for quote, plus 10 days for PR creation and approval and 4 weeks for purchase and delivery.
3. Issue – Link related jira ticket that the purchase is being requested for
4. Epic – If applicable, select related Jira Epic
5. Justification – Type answers under each of the 4 questions in the text box.
6. Quote Attached – If you have a quote, select Yes and attach the quote to the request using the Attachment section. Otherwise select No.
8. Items to Purchase – <Skip this step if you attach a quote> For each item requested, provide the quantity, description and if applicable, vendor and part number. You may attach a file containing this information such as a Bill of Materials (BOM).
9. Click Create to submit your request.
Once submitted, your request will be assigned to NSV Business Operations. You will be notified as updates are made to the request.
